      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Discord preflight filter and regression coverage to drop standalone bot-authored operational telemetry while preserving conversational bot messages.\n\nPR surface: Source +42, Tests +70. Total +112 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. by source inspection: enable Discord inbound debounce and bot messages, then send a telemetry-shaped bot line followed by a conversational bot mention from the same bot within the debounce window. The handler coalesces them into one synthetic preflight input and the new gate drops the batch.",
